覺成為支那滲透機器<br />\n就好似班仆街用大陸電話大陸app<br />\n你從事科研？只要你有家人就有得要脅你，你乜資料大陸都知道<br />\n好人好姐唔搞你？傻啦，賤種基因命運冇得變架"},{"pid":"e5d1cf2e3e9b55b16e12e8bd43943075b9ded86c","tid":562452,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"排華來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 什麼共享中國人榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd51f4f94d3717bf6066c44e42c6bb216cceb7e","tid":562452,"uid":10587,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6e2c50c7350ce96cb716d70f66fe52dd5782aa0b","tid":562452,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3acbc1f731a1512f94fbd81844ed48ba5719cf76","tid":562452,"uid":10587,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，玩種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國唔係出左預算啦咩，仲R funding?<br />\n不如話埋猶太人操控經濟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"咁都算種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"如果華人有猶太人咁高質，聽到佢咁講一早屌到美國跪低啦"},{"pid":"86684534d0f4c3e42bda1aba2ce99b47431987bb","tid":562452,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"今次真係移左民都被人當二等公民<br />\n<br />\n支持美國將捉鳩哂堆疑似<br />\n同支共有關係的中國人，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f0b482be258822fd43b6a182f6dd136c12acc9","tid":562452,"uid":77185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd51f4f94d3717bf6066c44e42c6bb216cceb7e","tid":562452,"uid":10587,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6e2c50c7350ce96cb716d70f66fe52dd5782aa0b","tid":562452,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3acbc1f731a1512f94fbd81844ed48ba5719cf76","tid":562452,"uid":10587,"like":3,"disli